column5: Was pretty nippy out there this afternoon, but managed a couple of pike.  My wife is away for a few days so I kept one for dinner, thought I'd share -  mmm...
nom nom nom! nice looking dinner!
what's going on in the picture right above the dinners head?
looks like someone farted and they are running for the door
Nice looking member of the hot oil brigade.
was there any bones left in it?
Nice... Nothern Pike are good eating.. I would know.. I had Pike for dinner tonight too
such a good tasting fish.....prepped right, it is one of my favourites.. good job!
Fantastic money shot! Pike are one of the best eating fish!!
YUM!  looks good!Cant wait till winter for some brookies!
Dude, that picture should be on a menu somewhere. Nice! Jim
